	<dl>
	<dt>mainly because I'm still 16, but I want...</dt>
	<dd><p>mainly because I'm still 16, but I want vote. So all the rest of you please vote and make it for the Lib Dems or even Respect because they both want to lower the voting age to  16.  DOn't be 'not apathetic' go out and vote so I and other teenagers like me can vote.</p>
	<small>
	written 30th Apr 2005 <!--  | <a href="../email/1642">Email this
    to a friend</a> | <a
    href="/abuse/?postid=1642">abusive?</a> -->
	</small>
	</dd>
	</dl>

